title: Senegal Money Supply M2
description: Money Supply M2 in Senegal decreased to 8572500 XOF Million in August from 8593900 XOF Million in July of 2022. Money Supply M2 in Senegal averaged 3271119.46 XOF Million from 2004 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 8593900 XOF Million in July of 2022 and a record low of 1051355 XOF Million in February of 2004. This page provides - Senegal Money Supply M2- actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Central Bank of West African States (BCEAO)
